{"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setreverseproxy:headers:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setReverseProxy:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSString"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"text":"url","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"headers:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSDictionary<NSString *,NSString *>","preciseIdentifier":"c:Q$objc(cs)NSDictionary"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"headers"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"url","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The full URL of your reverse proxy endpoint (e.g., “https:\/\/proxy.company.com\/pushwoosh”). Must not be nil or empty."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"headers","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Optional dictionary of custom HTTP headers. Pass nil if no custom headers are needed.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Routes all Pushwoosh SDK network requests through your own proxy server."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"This is useful for:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Enterprise security"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Route traffic through corporate proxies"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Regional compliance","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Ensure data flows through specific regions","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Network monitoring","type":"text"}]},{"text":": Inspect and log SDK traffic","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Firewall restrictions"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Work around corporate firewall rules"}]}]}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The proxy must forward requests to the appropriate Pushwoosh API endpoints"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"while preserving all headers and request body content."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Settings are not persisted and must be set on every app start."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"URL must start with https:\/\/ or http:\/\/.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom headers are only applied when reverse proxy is active."}]},{"text":"Example","anchor":"Example","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Configure proxy for enterprise deployment:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["class NetworkConfiguration {","","    func configureForEnterprise() {","        guard let proxyURL = Configuration.shared.pushwooshProxyURL else {","            return","        }","","        Pushwoosh.configure.setReverseProxy(proxyURL, headers: nil)","","        Logger.info(\"Pushwoosh configured to use proxy: \\(proxyURL)\")","    }","","    func configureForRegion(_ region: Region) {","        switch region {","        case .eu:","            Pushwoosh.configure.setReverseProxy(","                \"https:\/\/eu-proxy.company.com\/pushwoosh\",","                headers: [\"X-Auth-Token\": \"your-token\"]","            )","        case .asia:","            Pushwoosh.configure.setReverseProxy(","                \"https:\/\/asia-proxy.company.com\/pushwoosh\",","                headers: nil","            )","        case .us:","            break \/\/ No proxy needed","        }","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","roleHeading":"Type Method","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setReverseProxy:headers:"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"setReverseProxy:headers:","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setReverseProxy:headers:","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"title":"setReverseProxy:headers:"},"abstract":[{"text":"Sets a reverse proxy URL and optional custom HTTP headers for all SDK network requests.","type":"text"}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setReverseProxy:headers:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","title":"PWConfiguration","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}],"role":"symbol","abstract":[],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"title":"PushwooshCore","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","role":"collection"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setReverseProxy:headers:":{"fragments":[{"kin